<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title> CRUD System</title>
    <link href="~/css/bootstrap.rtl.min .css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 text-center">
                <h1 style="color: white;" >CRUD System</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">


                <h3 style ="color: white;">Project Overview</h3>
                <p style="color:darkorange; font-weight:bold;" ">
                   - This application is a page for registering students and Departments.<br>
                   - You can create a new account through it, or log in if you already have an account<br>
                   - The user can activate the remember me feature to keep the account logged in.<br>
                   - The student can register in the available Departments.<br>
                   - The student can see the students in the Department.<br>
                   - There are two types of users: a regular user (student) and admins.<br>
                   - Tasks that the admin can perform:<br>
                    1. Edit or delete a student<br>
                    2. Edit or delete a Department<br>
                    3. Create roles<br>
                    4. Assign roles to users<br>
                    5. Create accounts for admins
                </p>
                 
              
                 

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3 style ="color: white;">Technologies Used</h3>
                <ul style="color: darkorange;">
                    <li><strong>C#</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>OOP</strong> and <strong>SOLID</strong> principles</li>
                    <li><strong>LINQ</strong> for data querying</li>
                    <li><strong>Entity Framework Core</strong> for database management</li>
                    <li><strong>HTML5</strong> and <strong>CSS3</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>Bootstrap</strong> for responsive design</li>
                    <li><strong>JavaScript</strong> for client-side interaction </li>
                    <li><strong>MVC</strong> for application architecture</li>
                    <li><strong>Dependency Injection</strong> for managing dependencies</li>
                    <li><strong>Tag Helpers</strong> and <strong>Client-Side Validation</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>ViewData</strong>, <strong>ViewBag</strong>, <strong>TempData</strong></li>
                    <li><strong>Partial View</strong> for reusable components</li>
                    <li><strong>Generic Repository Pattern</strong> for data access</li>
                    <li><strong>Security (Authentication, Authorization) Using Identity</strong></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        
    </div>



